<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Le&on - Luxury Edits & Posters</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Raleway:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #fdfdfd;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f1c2c, #928dab);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            color: #d4c1ec;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #1f1c2c;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fdfdfd;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #928dab;
            color: #0a0a0a;
        }

        main {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffd700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        section p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .products {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2c2a36, #3a3750);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            width: 280px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            transition: transform 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .product-card img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .product-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffd700;
        }

        .product-card p {
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .product-card button {
            background: #ffd700;
            color: #0a0a0a;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .product-card button:hover {
            background: #e6c200;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #1f1c2c;
            color: #ffd700;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .products {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Le&on</h1>
        <p>Luxury Edits, Posters & Logo Designs for Modern Creators</p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#products">Products</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <h2>Welcome to Le&on</h2>
            <p>Elevate your digital content with our premium edits, posters, and logos. Each design is crafted for creators who want style, elegance, and impact.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Le&on</h2>
            <p>Le&on specializes in luxury digital designs that make your brand or personal projects stand out. We focus on detail, sophistication, and modern aesthetics.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="products">
            <h2>Our Luxury Products</h2>
            <div class="products">
                <div class="product-card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/280x180" alt="Trending Edit">
                    <h3>Premium Social Media Edit</h3>
                    <p>Exclusive, high-quality edits for Instagram, TikTok, and YouTube. Make your content irresistible.</p>
                    <button>Buy Now</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/280x180" alt="Poster Design">
                    <h3>Luxury Poster Design</h3>
                    <p>Elegant, high-end posters for events, campaigns, or personal branding. Impress instantly.</p>
                    <button>Buy Now</button>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/280x180" alt="Logo Design">
                    <h3>Elite Logo Design</h3>
                    <p>Custom logos with a luxury feel. Make your brand unforgettable and stylish.</p>
                    <button>Buy Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Email: info@leonedits.com</p>
            <p>Phone: +123 456 7890</p>
            <p>Instagram: @leon.edits</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2025 Le&on - Luxury Edits & Posters</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
